    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们想做一个用户旅程图，展示顾客在我们线上商城的完整购物流程。从进入网站开始，到把商品加入购物车为止。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Browsing the online shop",
        "Enter online shop",
        "Browse online shop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解了。那进入商城这部分，除了访问网站，登录环节要不要放进去？我们用的是FinTech_AuthVault做认证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Visit website",
        "Log in (FinTech_AuthVault)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "要的，登录步骤很重要，虽然体验评分可能不高，但得让用户看到这是必经环节。登录评分给3分吧，访问网站给5分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Log in (FinTech_AuthVault)",
        "Visit website"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，进入商城部分我先这样画。接下来浏览环节，用户会先滚动首页，然后查看商品分类，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scroll through start page",
        "Check out categories"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，但浏览流程还要更细一些。进入具体分类后，用户会应用筛选条件，然后滚动浏览产品列表，最后点进某个商品详情页。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go to category",
        "Apply filter to category",
        "Scroll through products",
        "Go to product"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "商品详情页里面，用户会看评价吗？还有产品规格变体这些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Read review",
        "Read another review",
        "Check out product variants"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "会的，这里有个细节——第一次看评价体验不太好，可能只有1分，但继续看第二条评价时体验回升到5分。看完规格变体后，最终把商品加入购物车，这一步给满分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Read review",
        "Read another review",
        "Check out product variants",
        "Add product to shopping cart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，整个旅程图我已经画完了。从进入线上商城到浏览分类、筛选产品、查看评价和规格，最后加入购物车，每个步骤的评分也都标注了。您看看还有什么需要调整的吗？",
